<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَلَوْ تَزَوَّجَتْ بِغَيْرِهِ وَدَخَل بِهَا ثُمَّ عَادَتْ إِلَيْهِ بَعْدَ ذَلِكَ، عَادَتْ إِلَيْهِ بِالْحِل الأَْوَّل، فَلاَ يَمْلِكُ عَلَيْهَا إِلاَّ مَا بَقِيَ مِنَ الطَّلاَقِ الَّذِي كَانَ ثَابِتًا لَهُ فِي ذَلِكَ الْحِل <span class="c2">(١)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>إِيلاَجٌ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> وَطْءٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>إِيلاَدٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرِ:</span> اسْتِيلاَدٌ، أُمُّ الْوَلَدِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>إِيلاَمٌ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">التَّعْرِيفُ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> الإِْيلاَمُ هُوَ:</span> الإِْيجَاعُ،<span class="c5"> وَالأَْلَمُ:</span> الْوَجَعُ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> .<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">الأَْلْفَاظُ ذَاتُ الصِّلَةِ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>أ -<span class="c5"> الْعَذَابُ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٢ -<span class="c5"> الْعَذَابُ:</span> هُوَ الأَْلَمُ الْمُسْتَمِرُّ، وَالأَْلَمُ قَدْ يَكُونُ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
